https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=23994	27720
NASA<a href="http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/NEEMO/neemolive.html">极端环境行动项目（NEEMO）</a>将派一组雇员和合同工到Aquarius水下实验室<a href="http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/145615/20110513/nasa-neemo-aquarius-underwater-laboratory-human-survival-space-exploration-asteroid-research-near-ea.htm">生活最多三周时间</a>，为未来太空探索做准备。<i>
